{"tid":1803913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【我爸是李剛】醉駕撞死人累爸爸被撤職　囂張「官二代」刑滿出獄落泊生活曝光","createTime":"2019-12-30T14:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T02:30:52.000Z","uid":215823,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"59ea92686054aabdf6842a349f18c01376a01c2b","tid":1803913,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"說出網絡金句「我爸是李剛」的內地囂張「官二代」李啟銘，2010年因醉駕撞倒2名女生，導致一死一傷，事後竟口出狂言「有本事你們告我，我爸是李剛！」令李剛登上各大熱搜榜成為風雲人物。兒子李啟銘最終被判入獄6年，去年刑滿出獄，但爸爸早已離家出走，他的生活亦不再富貴，並渴望尋父團聚。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地傳媒報道，2010年10月16日晚上，時年22歲的「官二代」李啟銘，駕駛黑色私家車駛至河北大學附近，因酒後駕駛撞倒2名女生，事後不顧而去，其中一名女生經搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n李啟銘的車輛很快被學生和保安攔截下來，他仍不知悔改，口出狂言。<br />\n<br />\n事件引起網民譁然，「李剛」亦登上各大熱搜榜，原來李剛只是河北省保定市公安局北市區分局副局長，因兒子的狂言帶擘他被封為「國產四大名爹」。外界紛紛批評李剛太溺愛孩子，令兒子受挫折時只求爸爸解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n數日後，李剛接受訪問向受害人及家屬道歉，但李剛之後被撤職，更離家出走至今杳無音訊。至於李啟銘被判入獄6年，從此兩父子不再相見。<br />\n<br />\n事隔9年，李啟銘於去年刑滿出獄，當時他表示對自己的行為感到後悔，承諾會改變自己，而最大的心願就是跟父母團聚一起吃頓飯。<br />\n<br />\n李啟銘至今出獄一年多，生活已歸於平淡低調，但李剛仍下落不明。目前李啟銘最渴望尋親成功，希望爸爸看到自己的改變，一家人重新開始。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79Wkj1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79Wkj1T.jpg&h=0ebca280&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMn32fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMn32fe.jpg&h=3a279774&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f599fe30021d91b1e340343d90cd87947815a2c1","tid":1803913,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:43:15.000Z","msg":"所以話<br />\n有個有錢老豆就會咁<br />\n平平淡淡過日子先係最快樂"},{"pid":"2256cc2098b6977f6b9a8ab1785df9e65ef01bdc","tid":1803913,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=edccb49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b63ae4db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要30000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=c34a70f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share條link去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"495368abae28e1fb03eaacb33a7e760daf03b334","tid":1803913,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"個老豆算有良心"},{"pid":"0775abe54c661d32f5fa2da488194e55aa3f5d49","tid":1803913,"uid":59818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"495368abae28e1fb03eaacb33a7e760daf03b334","tid":1803913,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:47:20.000Z","msg":"個老豆算有良心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"到佢唔落台咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3afbab8264ab70139d40752f25994d4a88cba7","tid":1803913,"uid":71237,"like":2,